{"tid":1562231,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[兄弟爬山係有用架!!] 有關曾偉雄入聯合國","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:46:34.000Z","uid":69473,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"766c204497f86ed1bfafd02198584a94ae09b4d4","tid":1562231,"uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"有件少少鼓舞嘅事同巴打絲打分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ey8ySMj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fey8ySMj.png&h=b6a3620a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片來源: facebook page : OIC 親子丼<br />\n<br />\n之前好多手足幫手聯署白宮，去反對曾偉雄條仆街入聯合國，多謝連登先！有巴打問聯合國嘅事好似同美國無關，唔知聯署有無用。的而且確美國無得直接否決個仆街入聯合國，但係<span style=\"color: red;\">今日見到有美國參議員表態反對啦！雖然係去動議叫Trump代表美國去反對，但至少暫時係睇到有「少少成效」。</span>我哋同樣唔肯定最後有無用，Trump會唔會出手，而白宮聯署又係咪100%有用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但好肯定同大家講，做咗一定比無做好！<br />\n做咗嘅話成功率會大過0，唔做就一定係0！<br />\n因為就算要人幫手，香港人都一定要話俾全世界知，從邊度幫，就等同我哋一直嘅本地、海外文宣，都係提高香港受關注度！</strong></span>而且對我哋嚟講，付出嘅成本真係幾分鐘，都係果句...<br />\n<br />\n以後見到白宮聯署，大家當然要望清楚內容先，然後<br />\n填表&gt;email確認&gt;分享俾朋友+推post！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=a03d89eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations</a><br />\n<br />\n仲可以繼續填架！10萬人係最低門檻，我哋一齊推個15萬，20萬！<br />\n<br />\n「有些事情不是因為看到希望才去堅持，而是因為堅持了才能看到希望。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醬油 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.foxnews.com/politics/sen-cruz-urges-trump-administration-to-block-chinas-next-un-power-play.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fsen-cruz-urges-trump-administration-to-block-chinas-next-un-power-play.amp&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=3dc24687\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.foxnews.com/politics/sen-cruz-urges-trump-administration-to-block-chinas-next-un-power-play.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目前香港被世界關注，例如美國開始嘗試用人權法製造壓力，或者今次曾偉雄聯合國事件。但大家緊記，不能鬆懈！一日未成功，一日都未完結！五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n狗官，黑警，必須付上責任！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀+推post<br />\n<br />\n請制裁香港政府及黑警於831之恐怖襲擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=783d159d\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國對香港進行人道救援<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=370f670d\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force</a><br />\n<br />\n通過人權法追究黑警性暴力<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-hk-police-sexually-assaulting-protestors-please-pass-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstop-hk-police-se